# Objective

Implement the **WorkspaceInstallation** aggregate exactly as defined by the approved CAP architecture.

The WorkspaceInstallation aggregate establishes the runtime deployment relationship between the **Platform Catalog** and the **Tenant Domain** by installing a published PlatformApplicationPackage into a TenantWorkspace.

WorkspaceInstallation is the runtime anchor for every deployed business application.

